        <mxCell id="162" value="Estrutura de pastas:
emals_consultoria/
  backend/         ← FastAPI, routers/, models.py, dre_engine.py
  frontend/src/    ← React pages, components, services/api.js
  frontend/dist/   ← build commitado (deploy sem Node no servidor)
  electron-client/ ← app desktop Electron
  release.ps1      ← script de deploy
  CLAUDE.md        ← arquitetura e convencoes (leia primeiro)
  ROADMAP.md       ← backlog oficial" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=#007ACC;fillColor=#e3f2fd;rounded=1;fontFamily=Segoe UI;fontSize=9;align=left;spacingLeft=8;spacingRight=8;" vertex="1" parent="103"><mxGeometry x="14" y="492" width="340" height="130" as="geometry"/></mxCell>

